category: serif
subsets: menu,latin

family: Lusitana

designer: Ana Paula Megda

approved: true
description: <p>Lusitana is inspired \
  by the type found in the 1572 \
  first edition of "The Lusiads", a Portuguese \
  epic poem by Luís Vaz de Camões. This \
  typeface is made for long texts at small sizes.</p>

font.Lusitana-Regular.ttf.style: normal
font.Lusitana-Regular.ttf.weight: 400

